{
  "text": "These data also show that other higher energy structures are not present in the experiments, based on the comparison of their calculated spectra with the experimental spectrum [CITATION_1] . d Calculated at the MP2(full)/6-311+G(2d,2p) level of theory using MP2(full)/6-31G* optimized geometries, Reference [CITATION_2] . e Calculated on MP2(full) single point energies, Reference [CITATION_3] . f Calculated on B3LYP single point energies, Reference [CITATION_4] . g Exp. Reference [CITATION_5] . Scheme 4. The ground-state conformer of the sodiated 2-thioutacil and 6-methyl-2-thiouracil, and its complexes with water molecule [CITATION_6] . Thus, it would be expected that in our experiments, the conformer 4 alone or both 4+4a are the precursors for [4SU]Na + (H 2 O) n = 1,2 . The Mulliken charge predicted [CITATION_7] for the Na + cation of the 4 structure is equal to 0.746e, and Na + is also the most favorable site for water attachment.",
